reviewText: STEPPING BACK IN TIME,HAY WHERE'S THE LEASHES?? I REMEMBER SEING THIS FLICK ON THE BIG SCREEN OF THE OLD TREATER IN HB WITH THE WILD AUDIENCE FUN FUN FUN NOT EXCEPTED BY TODAYS STANDARDS,BEFORE LEASHES ON THE BIG POINT A SNNKER SET WOULD TAKE OUT 80%OF THE CROWD ANT THE WOULD BE GONE FOR 15 MINUTES OR SO,NOW EVERYONE JUST POPS UP,PLUS WE WERE REALLY GOOD SWIMMERS!!
